sources.title: Wild Ones on Wheels (1962) RAY DENNIS STECKLER
sources.description:
It's Friday@PizzaFLIX 
Stars: Francine York, Edmund Tontini and Ray Dennis Steckler
Cinematographer: Ray Dennis Steckler
Director: Rudolph Cusumano

A jailbird named King Tut and his gang of beatnik punks scramble over hidden loot buried in the Mohave desert.  The incredibly strange filmmaker Ray Dennis Steckler steals the show with an early acting role.

metadata.Plot: A gang murders an ex-con and forces his wife to help them find $250,000 he had buried in the desert.
metadata.Actors: Francine York, Edmund Tontini, Robert Blair
